data.description: Welcome to one of the most sought after communities throughout Venice. This rare POOL home with 4 Bedrooms and 3 bathrooms is the perfect haven for all. Sitting just under 2,500 Sqft this prominent residence offers large open spaces, multiple living areas, full 3 car garage, and plenty of area for the entire family. Brand new high quality water resistant vinyl laminate in bedrooms and living room. As you enter, this home offers vaulted ceilings and beautiful crown molding throughout. The floorplan gives you views to the enclosed pool with built in spa and covered patio overlooking the lake where you can enjoy the Florida lifestyle at its finest. Brand new pool pump is being installed before closing. This gorgeous gated community has a resort style pool with a spa, fitness center, tennis courts, pickleball courts, basketball court, walking trails, beach volleyball, BBQ area, and a skating rink! Close to schools, beaches, and entertainment. Schedule your showings today.
